						<li><a class="icons icon-icons_email-top-share tagmanager" title="Share by Email" href="mailto:?subject=Sharing a story from Hakai Magazine&body=I thought you might find this story interesting:%0D%0A%0D%0ACan Animals Evolve Fast Enough to Keep Up with Climate Change?%0D%0AMaybe.%0D%0Ahttps://hakaimagazine.com/news/can-animals-evolve-fast-enough-to-keep-up-with-climate-change/" target="_blank"><span>Share by Email</span></a></li>



